  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/33bdf3a3e904a77383c19d494db4934e.avif?t=1754057708\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/6eba75d10a59c9df7c7367dbac2341de.poster.avif?t=1754057708\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/6eba75d10a59c9df7c7367dbac2341de.webm?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/6eba75d10a59c9df7c7367dbac2341de.mp4?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Samar is a young witch who works the spirit-swapping night shift in the eastern outskirts of Demashq. A recent spike in spirits crossing over from another dimension within the borders of the city has them puzzling over what’s going on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With friends needing help - and a popular band scheduled to kick off their big comeback tour in Demashq - Samar needs to work quickly before the city is overrun with stans and spirits alike!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/e36011c7c028dcedfe345279550e710f.poster.avif?t=1754057708\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/e36011c7c028dcedfe345279550e710f.webm?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/e36011c7c028dcedfe345279550e710f.mp4?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Spirit Swap: Lofi Beats to Match-3 To blends two major sources of inspiration: the joyful, colorful puzzle mechanics of Panel de Pon and the heartfelt and playful storytelling of visual novels/dating sims.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/244814061200996c9a2ba3759f006c83.avif?t=1754057708\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Swap to a custom lofi soundtrack</strong> by the incredible Meltycanon.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cast powerful spells</strong> by arranging spirits into special patterns to unlock potent powers.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bond with a diverse cast of witches and demons</strong>… and maybe even smooch.   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decorate your bedroom.</strong> Earn trinkets and keepsakes as you play, then place them to decorate Samar’s room.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoy unique game modes</strong>, including Endless and local Versus!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/9c43333b48b2c153301fdd6e98315951.poster.avif?t=1754057708\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/9c43333b48b2c153301fdd6e98315951.webm?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/9c43333b48b2c153301fdd6e98315951.mp4?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/33bdf3a3e904a77383c19d494db4934e.avif?t=1754057708\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/6eba75d10a59c9df7c7367dbac2341de.poster.avif?t=1754057708\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/6eba75d10a59c9df7c7367dbac2341de.webm?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/6eba75d10a59c9df7c7367dbac2341de.mp4?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Samar is a young witch who works the spirit-swapping night shift in the eastern outskirts of Demashq. A recent spike in spirits crossing over from another dimension within the borders of the city has them puzzling over what’s going on. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With friends needing help - and a popular band scheduled to kick off their big comeback tour in Demashq - Samar needs to work quickly before the city is overrun with stans and spirits alike!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/e36011c7c028dcedfe345279550e710f.poster.avif?t=1754057708\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/e36011c7c028dcedfe345279550e710f.webm?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/e36011c7c028dcedfe345279550e710f.mp4?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Spirit Swap: Lofi Beats to Match-3 To blends two major sources of inspiration: the joyful, colorful puzzle mechanics of Panel de Pon and the heartfelt and playful storytelling of visual novels/dating sims.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/244814061200996c9a2ba3759f006c83.avif?t=1754057708\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Swap to a custom lofi soundtrack</strong> by the incredible Meltycanon.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cast powerful spells</strong> by arranging spirits into special patterns to unlock potent powers.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bond with a diverse cast of witches and demons</strong>… and maybe even smooch.   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decorate your bedroom.</strong> Earn trinkets and keepsakes as you play, then place them to decorate Samar’s room.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoy unique game modes</strong>, including Endless and local Versus!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/9c43333b48b2c153301fdd6e98315951.poster.avif?t=1754057708\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/9c43333b48b2c153301fdd6e98315951.webm?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/9c43333b48b2c153301fdd6e98315951.mp4?t=1754057708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
